{"tid":1501122,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會唔會放棄有病但出過軌嘅男朋友？","createTime":"2019-08-24T09:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T09:49:47.000Z","uid":249341,"like":6,"dislike":334,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2a8a2ab89875a62921ab316e9293cd99fceb09","tid":1501122,"uid":249341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"男朋友有個病 (同佢一齊嘅時候已經知) 同佢一齊冇耐我就發現佢有同第二個女仔嘅曖昧對話 我嗰陣好嬲但係佢堅稱同個個女仔冇嘢所以我選擇左繼續一齊<br />\n<br />\n到今日我發現佢又同第二個女仔傾埋啲好曖昧嘅嘢 咩想同佢扑野 又話如果一齊係同一間房會對佢唔知做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲大大隻字話鍾意佢個個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我同佢攤牌嗰陣我男朋友話佢之前body check完 報告未出 但係有機會得返幾個月命 佢話佢主動contact啲 &ldquo;舊朋友&rdquo; 係想見佢哋最後一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地有病好慘㗎 開開心心咁同佢繼續落去當可憐佢啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一次不忠 百次不用 第一次出軌就應該飛左佢啦"},{"pid":"d9b674ecedd96ca12bcb2d594086f17ebd2c7f80","tid":1501122,"uid":249341,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:14:59.000Z","msg":"我真係好愛我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢平時對我真係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce44eaaaba046f7e4b78af3811abc448a229e13","tid":1501122,"uid":249341,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:15:35.000Z","msg":"成日睇護眼po 原來呢啲事真係可以發生係任何人身上<img src=\"/